title: Castro gives Astros lead in fifth inning (MLB - Major League Baseball)
text: ( Source : MLB - Major League Baseball ) HOUSTON -- After managing just one hit through their first four innings Sunday, the Astros came to life in the fifth, jumping on Royals right-hander Edinson Volquez for a pair of runs to take a 2-1 lead
